	 \     \                                          \
	  |/    |    command: track [<who>]                |
	       /    cost: 40 spell points                 /
	      |                                          |
	      |    Pick up the trail of the player or    |
	     /    monster  that you have  specified.    /
	    |    Be aware that evil intent may lead    |
	    |    you into dangerous places. Running    |
	     \    away or  casting track  without an    \
	      |    argument will break the spell.        |
	       \    Breaking the spell uses no mana.      \
